channel.title: Live: NASCAR Xfinity Racing Series
channel.desc: The NASCAR Xfinity Series Round of 8 rolls on with the United Rentals 250 from Talladega Superspeedway. Connor Zilisch picked up his 18th consecutive top-five finish Oct. 11 at Las Vegas. Sammy Smith, on the bubble in eighth, won this race in 2024.
